<lines>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_1">¶//Prius quam directè respondeam, duo</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_2">obserua pro praxi huius materiae valde</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_3">necessaria: primū est existente pretio le¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_4">gali illud esse sequendū, quia taxę eius</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_5">coniuncta est lex, &amp; praeceptum supe¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_6">riorum illo pretio in rep. omnes emere,</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_7">&amp; vendere iubentium. //Ita *@D. Th. 2. 2. q.</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_8">27. ar. 1.@ &amp; ibi eius expositores, @Caiet.@ @A¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_9">ragon@, @Bannes@, @Salon.@ @Reginaldus lib. 25.</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_10">cap. 16. sect. 3. n. 283.@* //Illo autem non</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_11">existente intrat pretium naturale cum</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_12">sua latitudine, quem omnes ementes, &amp;</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_13">vendantes sequi debent. //Tertio loco</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_14">naturali non currente in repub. subin¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_15">trat pretium conuentionale maiorem</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_16">latitndinem habens, quem iuxta bono¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_17">rum iudicium omnes sequi tenentur.</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_18">¶//Secundum est, pretium legale in indi¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_19">uisibili consistere, ita quod ne latum</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_20">quidem vnguem ab eo liceat discedere:</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_21">pretium verò naturale habere suam la¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_22">titudinem, intra quam licet emptori, &amp;</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_23">venditori carius, aut mitius contrahere.</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_24">//Pretium, denique conuentionale habet</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_25">multo maiorem latitudinem, verum</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_26">iuxta eam iudicio prudentium expensā</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_27">contrahendam est.</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_28">¶//De hoc ergo pretio conuentionali,</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_29">quod tātam habet latitudinem versatur</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_30">praesens dubium, vtrum possit in immē¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_31">sam excrescere Et quidē aliqua quocūq;</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_32">maiori, &amp; maiori pretio venire posse,</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_33">prout inter contrahentes conuenerit.</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_34">//Probatur primo, quia vnusquisq; suae rei</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_35">est moderator, &amp; arbiter, *l. in re man¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_36">data. C. mand. &amp; reg. iuris, &amp; l. etiam. §.</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_37">licet ff. 50. ma.* ergo si ambo contrahen¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_38">tes conueniant in pretio quantumuis</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_39">magno emptio, &amp; venditio constabunt,</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_40">non existente pretio legali, neque con¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_41">uentionali in rep. //Secundo, quia res</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_42">tantum valent quantum vendi possunt,</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_43">*l.1.§. si hęres ff. ad Trebel. &amp; ibi glos. &amp;</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_44">l. quaerebatur. ff. ad l. Falcid. &amp; l. debitum.</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_45">ff.ad Trebel. in fin.* sed hoc non obtinet</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_46">existente pretio legali, aut naturali, in</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_47">repub. quia illa pretia euidenter limita¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_48">ta sunt, &amp; arctis suis terminis conclusa,</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_49">ergo debet intelligi de pretio conuen¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_50">tionali. //Tertio, quia supponuntur con¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_51">trahentes conuenire scientes, &amp; volen¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_52">tes, ergo nemini, neque sibi ipsis faciūt</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_53">iniuriam, secundum regulam iuris [sciē¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_54">ti, &amp; volenti non fit iniuria.] //Quarto,</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_55">quia in casu supponimus non esse in re¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_56">publica pretium legale, neque natura¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_57">le, ergo necesse est ad conuentionale</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_58">recurrere. //Quinto, quia cum res hae</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_59">exquisitae, &amp; rarae non sint in rep. neces¬</line>
  <line id="tr_1_tl_60">sariae non cogitur empto emere, vnde</line>
</lines>
